ure]] \n| ''[[Think Like a Man (song)|Think Like a Man]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"I Don't Care\"<ref name=\"datpiff.com\"/>\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2014\n| [[Kid Ink]]\n| ''My Own Lane''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Help\"\n| [[Blackbear (musician)|blackbear]]\n| ''Help''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Am I Wrong\" \n| 2016\n|[[Berner (rapper)|Berner]]\n| ''Hempire''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"All on Me\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/mallys-world-vol-1/id1223181602|title=Mally's World, Vol. 1 by Mally Mall|work=[[iTunes]]|accessdate=July 9, 2017}}</ref>\n| 2017\n| Mally Mall, [[O.T. Genasis]]\n| ''Mally's World, Vol. 1''\n|}\n\n==Songwriter credits==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=text-align:left;\n|+ List of songs and singles written by Maejor\n! scope=col style=width:13em;| Title\n! scope=col style=width:4em; | Year\n! scope=col style=width:13em;| Artist(s)\n! scope=col style=width:13em;| Album\n|-\n! scope=row| \"About You\"\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2014\n| [[Trey Songz]]\n| ''[[Trigga (album)|Trigga]]''\n|-\n! scope=row| \"Hello World\"\n| rowspan=10 style=text-align:center;| 2013\n| [[Diggy Simmons]]\n| ''[[Unexpected Arrival]]''\n|-\n! scope=row| \"Only One\"\n| rowspan=2|[[Sammy Adams]] \n|rowspan=2|  Non-album singles\n|-\n! scope=row| \"Summertime\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Millionaire Misfits\n| rowspan=2| [[Iggy Azalea]]\n| rowspan=2| ''[[Glory (EP)|Glory]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Murda Bizness]]\"\n|-\n! scope=row| \"Say Somethin\"\n| [[Austin Mahone]] \n| Non-album single\n|-\n! scope=row| \"[[Love Me Like You Do]]\"\n| rowspan=2|[[Justin Bieber]]\n| rowspan=2|''[[Believe (Justin Bieber album)|Believe]]''\n|-\n! scope=row| \"[[One Love (Justin Bieber song)|One Love]]\"\n|-\n! scope=row| \"[[Windows Down]]\"\n| [[Big Time Rush]]\n| Non-album single\n|- \n! scope=row| \"Check Me Out\" \n| [[Trey Songz]]\n| ''[[Chapter V (Trey Songz album)|Chapter V]]''\n|-\n! scope=row| \"So Addicted\"\n| rowspan=4 style=text-align:cente