e 6 Mafia song)|Feel It]]\"\n| rowspan=6 style=text-align:center;| 2010\n| [[Three 6 Mafia]]\n| ''[[Laws of Power]]''\n|-\n! scope=row| \"[[Iyiyi]]\"\n| [[Cody Simpson]]\n|  ''[[4 U (EP)|4 U]]''\n|-\n! scope=row| \"[[She Got It Made (song)|She Got It Made]]\"\n| [[Plies (rapper)|Plies]]\n| ''[[Goon Affiliated]]''\n|-\n! scope=row| \"Great Expectations\"\n| [[Diggy Simmons]]\n| ''Airborne''\n|-\n! scope=row| \"[[Speakers Going Hammer]]\"\n| rowspan=2|  [[Soulja Boy]]\n| rowspan=2|''[[The DeAndre Way]]''\n|-\n! scope=row| \"[[Blowing Me Kisses]]\"\n|-\n! scope=row | \"On My Own\"\n| rowspan=3 style=text-align:center; | 2009\n| [[Chrisette Michele]]\n| ''[[Epiphany (Chrisette Michele album)|Epiphany]]''\n|-\n! scope=row| \"Black Roses\"\n| [[Trey Songz]]\n| [[Ready (Trey Songz album)|Ready]]\n|-\n! scope=row| \"Good Girls Like Bad Boys\"\n| [[Jadyn Maria]]\n| Non-album single\n|}\n\n==Releases under an alias==\n===As [[AREA21]] (with [[Martin Garrix]])===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Spaceships\"<ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/album/spaceships/1293742026 |title=\"Spaceships\" from Spaceships \u2013 Single by AREA21 |date=8 April 2016 |website=iTunes |access-date=31 January 2018}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2016\n| rowspan=\"6\" {{N/A|Non-album singles}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Girls\"<ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/album/girls/1293744154 |title=\"Girls\" from Girls \u2013 Single by AREA21 |date=20 May 2016 |website=iTunes |access-date=31 January 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"We Did It\"<ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/album/we-did-it/1249072584 |title=\"We Did It\" from We Did It \u2013 Single by AREA21 |date=23 June 2017 |website=iTunes |access-date=31 January 2018}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2017\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Glad You Came\"<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://itunes.apple.com/album/glad-